name: TRIBUTE TO LUCY ENIGMA
description:
*Psychedelic sagittarius guitar*
The guitar of a Sagittarius, owned only by Lucy Enigma! Not only does this guitar bring out a beautiful tone, but it's this guitar that always gives positive energy and new zest to Lucy Enigma!

*Transition* 
recorded at the end of 2019 at Kanawa Record Yogyakarta and assisted by Studio Engineer by Kemal Akbar. Guitar, Bass, Keys by Anggi, Mixing & amp Mastering by Aloysiusnitia.

must check out the outstanding original work of Lucy Enigma
